WEBVTT

00:01.679 --> 00:04.846
I'm pregnant.
You're going to be a father.

00:04.849 --> 00:06.717
I promised myself
that this disease

00:06.719 --> 00:08.387
would die with me.

00:08.389 --> 00:10.824
Sometimes promises
have to be broken.

00:10.826 --> 00:14.030
Maybe after the wedding,
I shouldn't stay in London,

00:14.032 --> 00:17.467
because maybe I could kiss
another patient.

00:17.469 --> 00:18.603
Divya.

00:18.605 --> 00:21.841
Miss Newberg and I
are moving in together.

00:21.843 --> 00:23.644
You invested in companies
that didn't exist.

00:23.646 --> 00:24.812
Okay, let's start there.

00:24.814 --> 00:26.113
Allegedly didn't exist.

00:26.115 --> 00:27.815
Yeah,
you're going to jail, dad.

00:27.817 --> 00:29.517
If you desire for your father

00:29.519 --> 00:31.785
to have a less stressful
environment,

00:31.787 --> 00:33.587
I can make those arrangements.

00:33.589 --> 00:35.656
I was just thinking,
I mean, it's been a while.

00:35.658 --> 00:37.391
Maybe we should get together.

00:37.393 --> 00:40.227
I'd like that.

00:40.229 --> 00:41.695
Marisa's not moving out, huh?

00:41.697 --> 00:43.797
No.
Looks like we are.

